==Finnish==
===Adjective===

''vittuuntunut'' 

A person experiencing [[vitutus]]. Some females may like to use the word ''[[kyrpiintynyt]]'' instead.

Derived from [[vittu]].

===Adjective: Comparative levels===

''vittuuntuneempi'' "more deeply annoyed [than someone, or at a previous time]". Seldom used but not uncommon

''vittuuntunein'' "most deeply annoyed [in the group in question]". Really seldom used, almost extinct.

